        {
            "id": 6327206,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 力麗店(5364)大跌7.17%，報12.95元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>力麗店(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5364:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5364\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5364-TW</a>)30日12:42股價下跌1元，報12.95元，跌幅7.17%，成交350張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>力麗店(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5364:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5364\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5364-TW</a>)所屬產業為觀光餐旅，主要業務為一般旅館(飯店旅館經營、籌建規劃、市場分析規劃)。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌3.13%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.57%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+19 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+19 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6327206",
